title: 23: What's a Micro Penis?
itunes:title: What's a Micro Penis?
description:
The boys discuss why Trevor's dog has anxiety, doing comedy shows in rehab centers, and of course, micro penises. They introduce two new segments: Sock Talk and Secret Sock. In these segments they talk about loyalty to your homie, drug cartels, and what to do if you're an inch inside your mom.

Want an EXTRA episode a week? Become an exclusive member on Patreon!
